<h1>Welcome to use the sign-in system, this is the instruction of teacher page.</h1>
<h3>1. Main Page</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can view the developer information on the right.
    <br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; On the left is the list of directories, which will be explained in the next section.
    <br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; The upper right shows your user name. Near the name, you can click on "Exit" button to log out.</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T1.png" alt="Main page" title="Main_page" width="1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>2. Manage student</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see your students' information (ID, student id, name and clazz) on Student List page. 
    <br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can also add, delete and edit their information. 
    <br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; If you want to search for certain student, you can enter their name and clazz and then click on "search" button. On the bottom right you can see the number of results.

</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T2.png" alt="Manage student" title="Manage student" width="1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>3. Manage teacher</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see your personal information on Teacher List page.
    <br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can also edit the information.
</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T3.png" alt="Manage teacher" title="Manage teacher" width="1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>4. Manage course</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see courses that you teach on Course List page.
	<br/> &nbsp;&nbsp;You can also add, delete and edit courses' information.
	<br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can use search function by the way that is the same as search in Student List.
</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T4.png" alt = "Manage course" title = "Manage course" width = "1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>5. Course selected</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see Course List that is the same as Course List in Manage course function.
</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T5.png" alt = "Course selected" title = "Course selected" width = "1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>6. Check-in</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see check-in information on Check-inList page.
	<br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see students and their check-in status.
	<br/> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can use search function by the way that is the same as search in Student List.
</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T6.png" alt = "Check-in" title = "Check-in" width = "1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>7. Manage password</h3>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp; You can see change your password here.</p>
<img src = "IntroductionImg/T7.png" alt = "Manage password" title = "Manage password" width = "1000"/>
<br/>
<h3>Thank you for reading! </h3>
    
